#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The configuration options available here are used as default by all &kde; "
"applications that use &sonnet;, which is a frontend to various free spell "
"checkers."
msgstr ""
"Ovde date postavne opcije podrazumevane su za sve KDE programe koji koriste "
"<application>Sonnet</application>, pročelje za razne slobodne pravopisare."

# rewrite-msgid: /GNU Aspell/Aspell/
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To use &sonnet; you need to install spell checkers like &eg; <ulink url="
#| "\"http://aspell.net/\">GNU Aspell</ulink>, <ulink url=\"http://hspell."
#| "ivrix.org.il/\">Hspell</ulink> or <ulink url=\"http://hunspell."
#| "sourceforge.net/\">Hunspell</ulink> and additionally the corresponding "
#| "dictionaries for your language."
msgid ""
"To use &sonnet; you need to install spell checkers like &eg; <ulink url="
"\"http://aspell.net/\">&GNU; Aspell</ulink>, <ulink url=\"http://hspell."
"ivrix.org.il/\">Hspell</ulink> or <ulink url=\"https://hunspell.github.io/"
"\">Hunspell</ulink> and additionally the corresponding dictionaries for your "
"language."
msgstr ""
"Da bi <application>Sonnet</application> radio, morate instalirati neki od "
"pravopisara, kao što su <ulink url=\"http://aspell.net/\">Aspell</ulink>, "
"<ulink url=\"http://hspell.ivrix.org.il/\">Hspell</ulink> ili <ulink url="
"\"http://hunspell.sourceforge.net/\">Hunspell</ulink>, kao i odgovarajuće "
"rečnike za željeni jezik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The configuration options selected here can be overridden by each "
"application."
msgstr "Ovde izabrane postavne opcije može potisnuti svaki program ponaosob."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the drop down box <guilabel>Default language</guilabel> choose from the "
"available dictionaries, which one to use for &sonnet;."
msgstr ""
"Iz padajućeg spiska <guilabel>Podrazumevani jezik:</guilabel>, između "
"raspoloživih jezika, birate onaj koji želite da <application>Sonnet</"
"application> koristi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:47
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Spell Options"
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opcije pravopisa"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable autodetection of language"
msgstr "Automatsko otkrivanje jezika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature is based on several heuristics (script used, trigram matching "
"and language ranking on available languages in the spell-checking backend). "
"This allows it to automatically switch language in a multi-language document."
msgstr ""
"Ova mogućnost je zasnovana na nekoliko heuristika (korišćeno pismo, "
"poklapanje trigrafa i rangiranje jezika po dostupnim jezicima u "
"pravopisarskoj pozadini). Pruža automatsku promenu jezika u višejezičkom "
"dokumentu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic spell checking enabled by default"
msgstr "Automatska provera pravopisa podrazumevano uključena"

# skip-rule: t-line
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a mark is placed in this checkbox, the spelling of words will be check in "
"your document as you type them. Misspelled will have a red line drawn under "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Ako se ova kućica popuni, reči će biti proveravane dok ih kucate u "
"dokumentu. Pogrešno napisane će biti podvučene crvenom linijom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Skip all uppercase words"
msgstr "Preskoči sve pisano velikim slovima"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a mark is placed in this checkbox, the spelling of any word which "
"consists of all capital letters will not be checked."
msgstr ""
"Ako se ova kućica popuni, neće biti proveravana nijedna reč koja se potpuno "
"sastoji od velikih slova."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is useful for document using a large number of acronyms. If this box is "
"left unchecked, most of those acronyms will be incorrectly marked. By "
"placing a mark in this checkbox, the acronyms will not be marked as "
"misspelled."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je korisno u dokumentima sa velikim brojem akronima. Ako se kućica "
"ostavi prazna, većina tih akronima biće označena kao nepravilne reči. Ako se "
"popuni, akronimi neće biti označavani kao nepravilni."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Skip run-together words"
msgstr "Preskoči spojeno napisane reči"

# well-spelled: морепловка
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is not checked, then words that appear in the dictionary "
"separately, but have been run together, are considered to be spelling "
"errors. Examples of such words are shutout, cannot, and blackout."
msgstr ""
"Ako je ova kućica prazna, reči koje se u tekstu nađu spojeno dok ih rečnik "
"navodi odvojeno biće smatrane pravopisnim greškama. Na primer, ako rečnik "
"sadrži „more“ i „plovka“, ali ne i „moreplovka“, onda će „moreplovka“ biti "
"označena kao nepravilna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking this box will help prevent applications from flagging website and "
"email addresses for spelling errors. These addresses often contain words run "
"together."
msgstr ""
"Popunjavanje ove kućice pomoći će u izbegavanju adresa e‑pošte i veb "
"sajtova, koje bi bile prijavljene kao nepravilne budući da često sadrže "
"spojene i nepostojeće reči."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:96
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Ignoring words"
msgid "Ignored words"
msgstr "Ignorisanje reči"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bottom half of the dialog box allows you to designate specific words "
"(they may be specialized terminology, proper names, &etc;) which should be "
"ignored by the spelling program."
msgstr ""
"U donjoj polovini dijaloga možete navesti određene reči (poput stručnih "
"izraza, ličnih imena, itd.) koje pravopisar treba da ignoriše."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding a word to the ignore list"
msgstr "Dodavanje reči na spisak ignorisanih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a word, type the word in the text box and click the <guibutton>Add</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Da dodate reč, otkucajte je u polju za unos i kliknite na dugme "
"<guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting a word from the ignore list"
msgstr "Brisanje reči sa spiska ignorisanih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a word, select the word in the listbox containing all the "
"currently ignored words by clicking on it with the &LMB;. Now click the "
"<guibutton>Remove</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Da uklonite reč, izaberite je iz padajućeg spiska koji sadrži trenutno "
"ignorisane reči, klikom na nju <mousebutton>levim</mousebutton> dugmetom "
"miša. Zatim kliknite na dugme <guibutton>Ukloni</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are happy with the changes, simply click <guibutton>Apply</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Kada ste zadovoljni izmenama, jednostavno kliknite na <guibutton>Primeni</"
"guibutton>"

# rewrite-msgid: /restores all values/restores all settings/
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on the <guibutton>Defaults</guibutton> button restores all values "
"to their default values."
msgstr ""
"Klik na dugme <guibutton>Podrazumevano</guibutton> vraća sve postavke na "
"podrazumevane vrednosti."
